---
title: Roasted Cauliflower & Crumbly Cheese Salad with Israeli Couscous & Smokey Aioli
description: We love the tender texture of Israeli couscous, each grain holds its shape and easily handles bold flavours. Combine that with spiced roasted veggies, crumbly cheese and crisp salad leaves for a salad to remember!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
